OL,3,CMan found guilty of stealing from
OL,4,CLockerbie bombing memorial
OL,6,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fstealing from a memorial to victims of
OL,8,Fthe Lockerbie air disaster.
OL,10,FDumfries Sheriff Court heard that
OL,11,FGraeme Little took donations from a
OL,12,Fbox at the Tundergarth Church outside
OL,13,Fthe town last summer.
OL,15,FThe 59-year-old was found guilty of
OL,16,Ftwo counts of theft.
OL,18,FThe court was shown footage of Graham
OL,19,FLittle entering the Memorial Room at
OL,20,FTundergarth Church near Lockerbie on
OL,21,Fthe 25 August last year.
