OL,3,CMan found guilty of stealing from
OL,4,CLockerbie bombing memorial
OL,6,FHe appeared to take money from the
OL,7,Fcollection box, returning five days
OL,8,Flater to do the same thing again.
OL,10,FThe main issue in court today was one
OL,11,Fof identity as the man in the footage
OL,12,Fhad dark hair and wasn't wearing
OL,13,Fglasses.
OL,15,FHowever, Little had grey hair and was
OL,16,Fwearing glasses when he appeared in
OL,17,Fthe dock today.
