OL,4,CLockerbie bombing memorial
OL,6,FUltimately, the sheriff agreed with
OL,7,Fthree witnesses who claimed that the
OL,8,Fman in the dock was the same person as
OL,9,Fthe man in the video footage.
OL,11,FAfter finding him guilty on both
OL,12,Fcounts of theft, the sheriff said the
OL,13,Fissue today wasn't the amount of money
OL,14,Fstolen, which wasn't specified, but
OL,15,Fthe nasty meanness of the offence.
OL,17,FLater is due to be sentenced in the
OL,18,Ffirst week of May.
